entries.journal_entry_description: The Skaak Tippers have one of the stolen Gungan artifacts. Recover the one they have.
entries.journal_entry_title: Recover the Gungan Artifact Stolen by the Skaak Tippers
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: One of the stolen Gungan artifacts is with the Skaak Tippers. The only way you'll find it is by first attacking their bunker. You might, at this point, sense a trend.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find the Local Skaak Tipper Leader, Tomi Skaak, and defeat him.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Defeat the Local Skaak Tipper Leader, Tomi Skaak
entries.task05_comm_message_text: Tomi Skaak didn't have da artifact. Search da bunker for it.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Search the Skaak Tipper bunker for the stolen artifact.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Find the Gungan Artifact in the Skaak Tipper Bunker
entries.task07_message_box_text: You found what looks like the resting place of the artifact, but it is no longer there. There is a note from Dee Skaak saying that she has the artifact at the Skaak Tipper cave near Deeja Peak.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Go to the Skaak Tipper cave near Dee'ja Peak and get the Gungan artifact from Dee Skaak.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Defeat Dee Skaak and Recover the Gungan Artifact
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Return to Boss Nass with the artifact.
entries.task10_comm_message_text: Da Skaak Tipper leader of dissen bunker, Tomi Skaak, bein' yousa target. He'll mostly likely have da artifact.
